Package owltools.gaf Description

Processing of GO Gene Association Files

This package contains gaf file parser GAFParser, and also contains GafObjectsBuilder to build Document Object Model from a gaf file. See owltools.gaf.GAFParserTest and owltools.gaf.GafObjectsBuilderTest classes to see examples how to use GafParser and GafObjectsBuilder classes.
